    <p style="border: solid 1px #1E90FF; background: #1E90FF; padding: 15px; margin: 0; text-align: justify; line-height: 23px; color: white; font-size: 18px"><marquee>MARI BERWISATA KE SELURUH PENJURU DUNIAAAA!!!</marquee></p>
    <style>
        body {
            background-image: url('https://iea.imgix.net/817ded0e-7bb6-4b79-b425-65e6f7b705f1/shutterstock_1484419673.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat&fit=min&q=80&rect=0%2C517%2C3840%2C1643&w=1800&h=770&fit=crop&fm=jpg&q=70&auto=format');
